		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />demakes aren't known for being super accurate to the original.<br /><br />even with 8k SRAM, you could have a 2d platforms style horizontal scrolling world of 14x16 blocks screens...so 36 screens wide.<br /><br />13x16 world is 39 screens wide.<br />12x16 world is 42 screens wide.<br /><br />That might be enough.

		

		</td>
